!!! 5
%html{lang: :en}
  %head
    %meta{charset: 'utf-8'}
    %meta{name: 'viewport', content: 'width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0'}
    %meta{name: 'apple-mobile-web-app-capable', content: 'yes'}

    %title
      'Mentoring NYC'

    %link{href: '//maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.2.0/css/bootstrap.min.css', rel: :stylesheet, media: :all}
    %link{href: '//maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.1.0/css/font-awesome.min.css', rel: :stylesheet, media: :all}
    %link{href: 'http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Merriweather:300,400italic|Droid+Serif:400italic|Crete+Round:400', rel: :stylesheet, media: 'all'}
    %link{href: '/css/application.css', rel: :stylesheet, media: 'all'}

  %body
    .container-fluid
      %header
        .row
          .col-xs-12
            .row
              .header.col-xs-10
                %h1
                  Mentoring NYC
            .row
              .mission.col-xs-12.text-center
                .row
                  .col-xs-12
                    .subtitle
                      Sharing

                .row
                  .col-xs-12
                    .title
                      Experience &amp; Craft

                .action
                  %button.btn.btn-warning
                    Signup

      .row
        .content.col-xs-12.text-center
          %h2
            Meet mentors in the community.

          .row
            .col-sm-2.hidden-xs
            .col-xs-12.col-sm-8
              %p
                The opportunities today are endless in our city.  Technology use is creating
                more options than many other fields and continues to increase year after year.
                Our goal is to nuture growth and skill in people who want to improve.  We believe
                by building a community of mentorship, this is only a conversation away.
            .col-sm-2.hidden-xs

          %h2
            What you can expect

          .row
            .col-xs-12
              %ul
                %li
                  Collaboration on projects
                %li
                  Introduction to people/communities
                %li
                  Demonstration of new concepts
                %li
                  Pair programming

          .row
            .col-xs-12.col-sm-6
              %h3
                As a Student

              %p
                You will be paired with a mentor who has knowledge in technology.

            .col-xs-12.col-sm-6
              %h3
                As a Mentor

              %p
                You will be paired with a student who is curious to learn.

